text: James Willis may refer to: *James Willis (American football) (born 1972), American football player and defensive coordinator *Jim Willis (baseball) (James Gladden Willis, born 1927), baseball pitcher *Jimmy Willis (James Anthony Willis, born 1968), English footballer *James Willis (admiral) (1923–2003), Royal Australian Navy officer *James Hamlyn Willis (1910–1995), Australian botanist ==See also== *
